{
  "texts": [
    "Overcoming these obstacles will require interdisciplinary collaboration, improved data sharing practices, and rigorous validation of AI systems in clinical settings [35].",
    "Our bibliometric review has several limitations.",
    "First, we focused solely on publications available in English.",
    "Second, we did not consider electronic preprints from the open-access repository ArXiv, which may have resulted in the omission of several relevant studies on AI and breast cancer diagnosis and prognosis; however, these preprints are not peer-reviewed.",
    "Third, our data extraction and analysis were limited to Scopus databases from January 1, 2000, to June 20, 2024, potentially excluding many articles related to AI and breast cancer diagnosis and prognosis published after June 20, 2024."
  ]
}